      - text: "You've acquired the legendary "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: Master Sword
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ",\nthat which seals the darkness. You feel that the\nsword itself delights to be in your possession...\n\nEven at this moment, Princess Zelda is within\nHyrule Castle, fighting to suppress the Calamity.\nShe endures, believing you will come for her...\n\nWill you be able to save her as you are now?"
